A baller is someone who 'has made it to the bigtime' (ref. '''''ball''' players'') Now refers to people who are 'living it large.' In casual language, it is often replaced with "hella b", meaning "hella baller". Baller is a high compliment, and has taken on a meaning similar to "cool".

Hella Baller

An up and coming baller in the Pacific Northwest is Garret Vincent.  Characterized by his pelvis dunk where he shoves the ball down his pants and climbs through the hoop, Vincent has been nicknamed the human nut-sack.  Standing proud and five feet, four inches, Garret has been compared to the skills of Magic Johnson.